high_descs: Turn right and then go left through the doorway, then right again, walking straight to the dead end, then left into the room with the desk.

Turn towards the mug without a computer on it.
Place the pen inside the mug on the desk.
Pick up the mug with the pen in it.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn right, go ahead a bit and turn right again into the countertop area.
Place the mug in the corner of the countertop to the right of the sink.
